# 📊 Excel Dashboard – HR Analytics

## 📌 Overview

This dashboard focuses on analyzing **HR data using Excel**.

It provides insights into **employee attrition, workforce distribution, salary trends, and overall employee performance**, helping HR teams make informed decisions.

---

## 🔍 Key Analysis

* Total employees and attrition rate
* Department-wise employee distribution
* Attrition analysis by job role and gender
* Salary and age group insights
* Work-life balance impact on attrition

---

## 📈 Dashboard Features

* Interactive filters for **Department, Job Role, and Gender**
* KPI cards for quick insights (Employees, Attrition Rate, Avg Salary, Avg Age)
* Visual charts for workforce and attrition trends
* Clean and business-friendly layout

